title: Regional variation in mineral content, cytotoxicity, and antioxidant activity ofAerodramus fuciphagusnests from different districts in Kelantan, Malaysia.
abstract: This study aimed to assessAerodramus fuciphagus(Thunberg, 1812) nest's mineral content, cytotoxicity effects, and antioxidant activity. The Edible birds' nests (EBNs) were obtained from Tanah Merah (TM), Tumpat (TU), and Jeli (JE) districts in Kelantan, Malaysia.
journal: Journal of advanced veterinary and animal research
